{"tid":1126020,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"音樂已下「Jennie左右晃不跳舞」　Jisoo嚇傻轉頭…影片曝光粉絲心疼","createTime":"2019-04-26T05:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T01:56:04.000Z","uid":74065,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f3cea656f9da6be1afa6b9ad649747b1009541c2","tid":1126020,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:47:00.000Z","msg":"韓團BLACKPINK世界巡演來到第二階段於北美周各地區的表演，怎料24日芝加哥場唱到《DON'T KNOW WHAT TO DO》的時候，只見Jennie不停左右張望且完全沒有舞蹈動作，就這樣在舞台上徘徊了將近1分鐘的時間，粉絲後來才透過影片知道原因。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4051/4051941.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4051%2F4051941.jpg&h=f05795e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BLACKPINK世界巡演分為五階段，目前在第二階段的北美洲。（圖／翻攝自BLACKPINK IG）<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK在24日舉行了芝加哥場演唱會，正當氣氛來到最高點時她們開始演唱最新專輯收錄曲《DON'T KNOW WHAT TO DO》，不過背景音樂都已經響起，Jisoo、Rose和Lisa都開始舞蹈和走位，只見Jennie手扶著衣服在舞台上繞了一圈，沒按照動線蹲在自己位置上時，讓Jisoo也露出驚慌的表情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4051/4051946.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4051%2F4051946.jpg&h=fa929cf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Jennie在舞台上徘徊不跳舞。（圖／翻攝自Don Keybals YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n隨著舞蹈越來越激烈、動線不停更換到了副歌時，Jennie突然轉身走向後台消失了大約30秒的時間，只見她表情變得游刃有餘又專業，可能是對前面沒能完整表演感到抱歉，帶動氣氛時更加賣力。大多數的粉絲一直到後來才透過影片知道原來當時Jennie胸前的衣服迸開，一放手可能就會走光，心疼道「服裝出狀況後一定很慌張」、「Jennie肯定嚇很大一跳，希望服裝造型組以後不要再讓這種事情發生了」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4051/4051947.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4051%2F4051947.jpg&h=36389c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Jennie回來後就恢復正常舞蹈。（圖／翻攝自Don Keybals YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n▼190424 BLACKPINK - DON'T KNOW WHAT TO DO。（影片／取自Don Keybals YouTube，如遭刪除請見諒）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UoBzjhBbqwU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUoBzjhBbqwU&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=faa8cd1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UoBzjhBbqwU</a><br />\n<br />\nJENNIE心諗:今次又仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161354da5728f8d4afc5f292a5a24f230c2ddcf8","tid":1126020,"uid":213300,"like":50,"dislike":4,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:59:02.000Z","msg":"小公主咪做得啱囉<br />\n首歌叫don't know what to do呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ade937e26919d08f740df929e7db355455ad7f8","tid":1126020,"uid":136738,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T06:04:52.000Z","msg":"老闆娘緊系唔系負責條啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc94da883d4bc944e0f2082cf69127ec23bda0d2","tid":1126020,"uid":58335,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T06:06:24.000Z","msg":"等睇anti睇完標題又高潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51fd995c2bfb7d75085e36a983ff876c9020bdd4","tid":1126020,"uid":213300,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bc94da883d4bc944e0f2082cf69127ec23bda0d2","tid":1126020,"uid":58335,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T06:06:24.000Z","msg":"等睇anti睇完標題又高潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"ching又變番blink啦?"},{"pid":"e865b30e56cea08a8447800145ea5c09836a026e","tid":1126020,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T06:11:31.000Z","msg":"一睇就知係服裝嘅問題"},{"pid":"df8833ba78bf92969ed755b28aec6918ecd55c23","tid":1126020,"uid":58335,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"51fd995c2bfb7